If both the <code>version</code> and <code>preferred_versions</code> arguments are not configured, the data source will return the default version for the engine.</p>
</dd><dt class="property-optional"
            title="Optional">
        <span id="version_yaml">
<a data-swiftype-name="resource-property" data-swiftype-type="text" href="#version_yaml" style="color: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;">version</a>
</span>
        <span class="property-indicator"></span>
        <span class="property-type">String</span>
    </dt>
    <dd><p>Version of the DB engine. For example, <code>1.0.1.0</code>, <code>1.0.2.2</code>, and <code>1.0.3.0</code>. If both the <code>version</code> and <code>preferred_versions</code> arguments are not configured, the data source will return the default version for the engine.</p>
</dd></dl>
</pulumi-choosable>
</div>
